      • getCommonRevisionWithShortestPath

        public static String getCommonRevisionWithShortestPath(String revision1,
                                       String revision2)
        Get the common revision of the specified revisions which has the shortest path to the two. To ensure wise results the revisions should be terminal branch nodes.
        Parameters:
        revision1 - the first revision should be a terminal branch node
        revision2 - the second revision should be a terminal branch node
        Returns:
        the nearest common revision

        Returns:

        Create a merged revision.
        Parameters:
        graphName - the graph name
        branchNameA - the name of branch A
        branchNameB - the name of branch B
        user - the user
        commitMessage - the commit message
        graphNameDifferenceTripleModel - the graph name of the difference triple model
